<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.7">
<l>eḻumaik kumeṉa tāvik kiṉṉamu tatti ṉaiyeṉa tāruyir</l>
<l>keḻumi yakatirc cōti yaimaṇi vaṇṇa ṉaikkuṭak kūttaṉai</l>
<l>viḻumi yavama rarmu ṉivarvi ḻuṅkuṅ kaṉṉal kaṉiyiṉait</l>
<l>toḻumiṉ tūyama ṉatta rāyiṟai yunnil lātuya raṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sweet ambrosia of my soul for seven births, my precious life,</l>
<l>the full-rayed light, the one of sapphire-colour, the pot dancer,</l>
<l>the sugarcane fruit that is swallowed by excellent immortals [and] sages,</l>
<l>him worship, being pure of mind. [Your] affliction will not stay for a moment.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
